                   <img src="/Files/MainImages/mainImage4.jpg" class="d-block w-100">
                   <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                     <h2>КАРТРИДЖИ ОТ WJX И MAST PRO</h2>
                     <p>TATOO STORE</p>
